item.title: Pixel 5 Imei Repair Guide
item.description: The Reason The info on how to repair imei on pixel 5 is quite sparse and I needed a day of hacking around to actually do it. Im writing this guide to maybe help another soul that is on this same journey for some reason. Hopefully this helps. Have a great day fella <3 How To do It - unlock bootloader (this will wipe the device, make sure you have backup) - downgrade the system to earliest possible firmware (redfin-rd1a.
